title: CL: Real Madrid play out goalless draw with Paris Saint Germain
text:
*London:* Real Madrid failed to continue their winning momentum as they were held to a frustrating goalless draw against Paris Saint Germain (PSG) in their Champions League clash.
Despite dominating the match for most of the time, Real failed to take the ball past the goal post, the Guardian reported.*Cristiano Ronaldo (C) ... Â»
